    "body": "Hello up there. I hit Cython bug where `nullptr` is not treated exactly as `NULL`. Please find below a short example that demonstrates the problem. Thanks beforehand, Kirill.\r\n\r\n--------\r\n\r\nThe following module compiles just fine:\r\n\r\n```pyx\r\n# distutils: language=c++\r\n# cython: language_level=2\r\n\r\ncdef cppclass MyClass nogil:\r\n    int* p\r\n\r\n    __init__():\r\n        this.p = NULL\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever the following one fails:\r\n\r\n```pyx\r\n# distutils: language=c++\r\n# cython: language_level=2\r\n\r\nfrom libcpp cimport nullptr\r\n\r\ncdef cppclass MyClass nogil:\r\n    int* p\r\n\r\n    __init__():\r\n        this.p = nullptr     # NOTE nullptr instead of NULL\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ cythonize -i nullcxx.pyx \r\nCompiling /home/kirr/tmp/trashme/nullcxx.pyx because it changed.\r\n[1/1] Cythonizing /home/kirr/tmp/trashme/nullcxx.pyx\r\n\r\nError compiling Cython file:\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n...\r\n\r\ncdef cppclass MyClass nogil:\r\n    int* p\r\n\r\n    __init__():\r\n        this.p = nullptr\r\n                ^\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nnullcxx.pyx:10:17: Cannot assign type 'nullptr_t' to 'int *'\r\nTraceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"/home/kirr/src/wendelin/venv/z-dev/bin/cythonize\", line 11, in <module>\r\n    load_entry_point('Cython', 'console_scripts', 'cythonize')()\r\n  File \"/home/kirr/src/tools/py/cython/Cython/Build/Cythonize.py\", line 224, in main\r\n    cython_compile(path, options)\r\n  File \"/home/kirr/src/tools/py/cython/Cython/Build/Cythonize.py\", line 77, in cython_compile\r\n    **options.options)\r\n  File \"/home/kirr/src/tools/py/cython/Cython/Build/Dependencies.py\", line 1098, in cythonize\r\n    cythonize_one(*args)\r\n  File \"/home/kirr/src/tools/py/cython/Cython/Build/Dependencies.py\", line 1221, in cythonize_one\r\n    raise CompileError(None, pyx_file)\r\nCython.Compiler.Errors.CompileError: /home/kirr/tmp/trashme/nullcxx.pyx\r\n```\r\n\r\nCython version: `0.29.14-629-ga73815042` (today's master)\r\n\r\nPossibly related issue: https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/3020",
